description: Oklahoma City's Crepe Brewers is bringing this Parisian delicacy curbside to the states! Got a sweet-tooth or in the mood for something salty? Either way, your curb your appetite with a sweet or savory crepe. Popular savory crepes include the smoked salmon crepe and the prosciutto pear crepe. Sweet crepes include strawberries and cream, peanut butter banana bliss, and more.
name: Crepe Brewers
